[b]TVO - Allan Gregg in Conversation, October 17 2008: Eric Margolis on 'American Raj: Liberation or Domination?'[/b]

He is one of Canada's most experienced -- and outspoken -- commentators on the Middle East. Author and syndicated columnist [url=http://www.ericmargolis.com/]Eric Margolis[/url] has long been a critic of American foreign policy and of Canada's military involvement in Afghanistan. His new book is called [url=http://www.keyporter.com/BookDetail.aspx?ISBN=1554700876]American Raj: Liberation or Domination?[/url]

